quran[9{c,v,t}:
21,36,aur jab kafir tum ko dekhte hain to tum seistehzaa karte hain kekiya yahi shakhs hai jo tumahray mabodon ka zikar ( buraiee se )kiya karta hai halaank woh khud rehman ke naam se munhkir hain
21,37,ensaan ( kuch aisa jald baz hai ke goya ) jald baazi hi se banaya gaya hai. mein tum logon ko anqareeb apni nishanain dukhao ga to tum jaldi nah karo
21,38,aur kehte hain ke agar tum sachey ho to ( jis azaab ka ) yeh vayd ( hai woh ) kab ( aeye ga ) ?
21,39,ae kash kafir is waqt ko jaanen jab woh apne monhon par se ( dozakh ki ) aag ko rok nah saken ge aur nah apni pithon par se aur nah un ka koi madadgaar hoga
21,40,balkay qayamat un par nagahan aa waqay hogi. aur un ke hosh kho day gi. phir nah to woh is ko hata saken ge aur nah un ko mohlat di jaye gi
21,41,aur tum se pehlay bhi payghambaroon ke sathistehzaa hota raha hai to jo log un mein se tamaskhurkiya karte they un ko isi ( azaab ) ne jis ki hansi uratye they aa ghera
21,42,kaho ke raat aur din mein khuda se tumhari kon hifazat karsaktha hai? baat yeh hai ke apne perwar-digaar ki yaad se munh phairay hue hain
21,43,kiya hamaray siwa un ke aur mabood hain ke un ko ( masaaib se ) bacha sakayn. woh aap apni madad to kar hi nahi satke aur nah hum se panah hi diye jayen ge
21,44,balkay hum un logon ko aur un ke baap dada ko mtmta karte rahay yahan taq ke ( isi haalat mein ) un ki umrein busr hogyin.kiya yeh nahi dekhte ke hum zameen ko is ke kinaroon se ghutatay chalay atay hain. tokiya yeh log ghalba panay walay hain ?
